{"tid":177854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（義士）向警擲膠樽囚9個月，熱狗上訴駁回繼續服刑","createTime":"2017-03-29T06:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T07:25:29.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a67db6caee22167dfb03bb5243fee43f5352f15","tid":177854,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"去年大年初二凌晨旺角發生騷亂，熱血公民成員陳柏洋當晚涉兩度向警員投擲膠水樽，隨後激烈拒捕，經審訊後襲警及拒捕罪成，判囚9個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳不服定罪及判刑早前提上訴，法官今駁回兩者的上訴，服刑三個月後獲准保釋的陳，須即時還柙繼續服刑。"},{"pid":"784eb91d7f31d4689e77c554956dbbbf3574e5a1","tid":177854,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170329/large/1490764217_e563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F1490764217_e563.jpg&h=e2b96f7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32d1375eb1372df22570c1dc57f82098e93b1108","tid":177854,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"政治庛護"},{"pid":"e9697b7859793fc3b5499876454f7579a8f61fbd","tid":177854,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac349d2181a739edc0f5df78e9e69fb9512232dd","tid":177854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政治庛護</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}